			(property "Description" "TIANBO HJR-4102-N-12V, 6-pin DIL SPDT (1 Form C). Coil 5,8 (~320R). Common 1&12 tied. Contacts: pin 6 = NO, pin 7 = NC (per datasheet, confirmed by continuity on WF26). No internal flyback diode per datasheet."
